65
00:05:27.167 --> 00:05:29.875 line:82%
The words are "Pritam come hither."

66
00:05:30.458 --> 00:05:34.333 line:82%
The song is specially requested by
our neighbor, Chaddaji from Queens.

67
00:05:35.850 --> 00:05:37.142 line:82%
That's very kind of you.

68
00:05:37.798 --> 00:05:40.978 line:82%
Kammo... Vimmo...

69
00:05:42.249 --> 00:05:44.159 line:82%
-Go Lajjo...
-Go Lajjo...

70
00:05:44.459 --> 00:05:49.167 line:82%
Pritam, come hither.

71
00:05:49.905 --> 00:05:54.875 line:82%
Pritam, come hither.

72
00:05:55.083 --> 00:05:58.833 line:82%
My sad heart calls out to you.

73
00:06:05.708 --> 00:06:09.542 line:82%
Grandmother? Grandmother, stop it!

74
00:06:09.840 --> 00:06:11.895 line:82%
Oh God! You interrupted our prayers?

75
00:06:12.075 --> 00:06:13.333 line:82%
Insulted the goddess?

76
00:06:13.417 --> 00:06:15.625 line:82%
-Don't you have any shame?
-Don't you have any shame?

77
00:06:15.750 --> 00:06:17.542 line:82%
Singing "Come hither" to Chaddaji?

78
00:06:17.667 --> 00:06:20.250 line:82%
Who's singing it to Chaddaji?
We are singing "Pritam, come hither."

79
00:06:20.458 --> 00:06:22.583 line:82%
- What is his first name?
- Pritam--

80
00:06:24.632 --> 00:06:26.452 line:82%
- And what is this?
- What?

81
00:06:26.573 --> 00:06:27.635 line:82%
This.

82
00:06:28.042 --> 00:06:30.708 line:82%
Wow! Pictures from Kunwari Kudi!

83
00:06:30.792 --> 00:06:33.000 line:82%
All three of them are so good-looking.

84
00:06:33.083 --> 00:06:34.875 line:82%
Three? They look like the same guy.

85
00:06:35.042 --> 00:06:36.292 line:82%
No, no. They are different.

86
00:06:36.375 --> 00:06:38.167 line:82%
Now what is that Kunwari Kudi ad?

87
00:06:39.917 --> 00:06:43.083 line:82%
Hey girl, hey girl, hey girl,
choose your groom and be free.

88
00:06:43.167 --> 00:06:44.708 line:82%
Choose one, two or three.

89
00:06:47.250 --> 00:06:50.667 line:82%
Grandmother! I am not interested
in marrying anyone, one, two or three.

90
00:06:50.958 --> 00:06:53.375 line:82%
If you don't marry,
my child, how will you have children?

91
00:06:53.708 --> 00:06:55.958 line:82%
I can have children.
There's no need to marry.

92
00:07:01.208 --> 00:07:03.292 line:82%
My brother Shiv, a handicap.

93
00:07:03.855 --> 00:07:06.500 line:82%
He couldn't play basketball
like the other boys,

94
