like the other boys.

95
00:07:10.687 --> 00:07:12.677 line:82%
Shiv, put off the T.V.

96
00:07:12.758 --> 00:07:14.167 line:82%
Whenever I see,
it's always basketball!

97
00:07:14.333 --> 00:07:16.875 line:82%
Just because I can't play,
doesn't mean I can't see.

98
00:07:17.490 --> 00:07:20.135 line:82%
Don't get cute with me.
All right. Hurry up.

99
00:07:20.250 --> 00:07:21.500 line:82%
Gia, help him.

100
00:07:21.708 --> 00:07:24.667 line:82%
-Didi, did you see my new dolls?
-Gia!

101
00:07:25.125 --> 00:07:27.833 line:82%
This is Mother, this is you,

102
00:07:28.917 --> 00:07:32.625 line:82%
