103
00:07:33.292 --> 00:07:34.500 line:82%
You are awake!

104
00:07:34.920 --> 00:07:36.333 line:82%
Looking so good, like Hari Putter.

105
00:07:36.458 --> 00:07:38.333 line:82%
Harry Potter, grandmother.

106
00:07:38.417 --> 00:07:39.458 line:82%
Whatever, it's all the same.

107
00:07:39.542 --> 00:07:41.208 line:82%
- Good morning, grandmother.
- OK. OK.

108
00:07:41.292 --> 00:07:42.292 line:82%
What are you doing today?

109
00:07:42.375 --> 00:07:45.750 line:82%
Grandmother's love for Shiv was only
matched by her hatred for Gia.

110
00:07:46.667 --> 00:07:51.500 line:82%
Gia was adopted and probably that's why
she did not consider her our own.

111
00:07:52.208 --> 00:07:56.595 line:82%
And Gia, she always kept the grandmother
doll away from her perfect family.

112
00:07:57.625 --> 00:07:59.250 line:82%
Distance was not just
between the two in the family,

113
00:07:59.625 --> 00:08:02.333 line:82%
