what will happen to these children?

132
00:09:02.667 --> 00:09:04.458 line:82%
I'm very concerned about them.

133
00:09:04.542 --> 00:09:07.078 line:82%
And I'm concerned only about them.

134
00:09:07.165 --> 00:09:09.417 line:82%
Yes, of course,
why would you be concerned about me?

135
00:09:09.500 --> 00:09:12.167 line:82%
Who am I to you?
If only my son was alive today--

136
00:09:12.250 --> 00:09:13.680 line:82%
Only if he was alive.

137
00:09:13.926 --> 00:09:15.600 line:82%
Stop it. Just stop it.

138
00:09:16.300 --> 00:09:19.542 line:82%
Here's your dollar. You won.
As usuaI, are you happy now?

139
00:09:19.780 --> 00:09:22.202 line:82%
And both of you...just forget it.

140
00:09:22.750 --> 00:09:24.625 line:82%
My morning began the same way everyday.

141
00:09:25.167 --> 00:09:29.792 line:82%
Mama and Grandmother's fight,
followed by my angry walkout,

142
00:09:30.583 --> 00:09:33.875 line:82%
and then listening to my stupid neighbor,
Sweetu's, stupid chatter.

143
00:09:40.583 --> 00:09:41.708 line:82%
And what will you have?

144
00:09:41.792 --> 00:09:46.250 line:82%
Sweetu. Full name, Jasprit Kapoor.
Kapoor with two O's.

145
00:09:46.750 --> 00:09:48.917 line:82%
My neighbor,
and unfortunately best friend.

146
00:09:49.208 --> 00:09:52.375 line:82%
She has two problems.
The weight that she never loses,

147
00:09:52.458 --> 00:09:54.538 line:82%
and the fact
that she never feels sad about it.

148
00:09:54.629 --> 00:09:57.058 line:82%
- TeII, Na...
- One doubIe expresso pIease.

149
00:09:57.625 --> 00:10:00.000 line:82%
