and you get the guy.

156
00:10:15.500 --> 00:10:17.167 line:82%
And what have you written about yourself?

157
00:10:17.250 --> 00:10:19.458 line:82%
- I have written the truth.
- What did you write?

158
00:10:19.583 --> 00:10:21.250 line:82%
That from far,
I look like Aishwarya Rai.

159
00:10:21.333 --> 00:10:23.250 line:82%
And up close,
like Aishwarya Rai's house.

160
00:10:33.208 --> 00:10:36.265 line:82%
- Sweetu, look at me.
- I see you everyday.

161
00:10:36.366 --> 00:10:39.322 line:82%
- He's so cute. He's so hot.
- Shut up.

162
00:10:39.417 --> 00:10:41.745 line:82%
All you are interested in is boys.

163
00:10:42.135 --> 00:10:44.542 line:82%
What will happen?
You will get the boy you want,

164
00:10:44.667 --> 00:10:46.542 line:82%
you will get married,
you will have his children and then,

165
00:10:46.625 --> 00:10:48.417 line:82%
