166
00:10:49.042 --> 00:10:51.035 line:82%
What will you do then?

167
00:10:51.917 --> 00:10:54.500 line:82%
I will marry again. What else?

168
00:10:56.195 --> 00:10:58.055 line:82%
Forget it!

169
00:10:58.146 --> 00:11:02.370 line:82%
Naina, my didi is right.

170
00:11:03.001 --> 00:11:04.495 line:82%
Babe's you need help.

171
00:11:05.115 --> 00:11:06.500 line:82%
You and your didi!

172
00:11:13.337 --> 00:11:15.585 line:82%
Bloody...

173
00:11:15.686 --> 00:11:17.833 line:82%
These people are eating all our business!

174
00:11:19.958 --> 00:11:23.000 line:82%
Jazz. Full name, Jaswinder Kapoor.

175
00:11:23.375 --> 00:11:27.292 line:82%
Sweetu's elder sister and unfortunately,
Mama's best friend and restaurant partner.

176
00:11:27.525 --> 00:11:29.125 line:82%
She had a problem too.

177
00:11:29.375 --> 00:11:31.000 line:82%
Youth, that she is desperately
holding on to.

178
00:11:31.083 --> 00:11:33.103 line:82%
