179
00:11:38.144 --> 00:11:41.593 line:82%
- Customers!
- Hey, three coffee. please.

180
00:11:41.704 --> 00:11:42.768 line:82%
Coming up!

181
00:12:04.417 --> 00:12:08.282 line:82%
