182
00:12:15.985 --> 00:12:18.165 line:82%
Look, I said I'm sorry Jenny.

183
00:12:18.546 --> 00:12:22.256 line:82%
- It's okay.
- It's not okay.

184
00:12:22.687 --> 00:12:24.708 line:82%
With great difficulty,
we have four or five customers coming in.

185
00:12:24.833 --> 00:12:27.237 line:82%
Thanks to you, if they run away,
what are we going to do?

186
