Then, what are we going to do.
I mean what... Just go!

190
00:12:51.488 --> 00:12:54.250 line:82%
Oh god! This rain.
I hate this rain.

191
00:12:54.927 --> 00:12:59.240 line:82%
- Naina!
- Opps! Sorry. That's my friend.

192
00:12:59.341 --> 00:13:00.833 line:82%
