193
00:13:09.060 --> 00:13:10.080 line:82%
Meet Rohit Patel.

194
00:13:10.710 --> 00:13:12.875 line:82%
Son of Karsanbai & Sarlaben Patel.

195
00:13:13.458 --> 00:13:16.167 line:82%
Karsanbai was one of the richest Gujaratis
in America.

196
00:13:16.750 --> 00:13:19.292 line:82%
His food chain was quite popular
in the whole country.

197
00:13:19.750 --> 00:13:21.750 line:82%
Name, "Dial a Dhokla".

198
00:13:22.208 --> 00:13:23.750 line:82%
Rohit lived alone in New York.

199
00:13:24.042 --> 00:13:27.667 line:82%
As for work, in the last three years,
