200
00:13:27.746 --> 00:13:29.367 line:82%
Hi guys. Have fun.

201
00:13:29.448 --> 00:13:30.959 line:82%
- Yes, Thank you.
- Good.

202
00:13:31.974 --> 00:13:34.796 line:82%
Okay. So, if I can get this fiIe
with this...

203
00:13:34.877 --> 00:13:36.752 line:82%
Ah JuIia!

204
00:13:37.363 --> 00:13:38.760 line:82%
Dinner at 8?

205
00:13:38.834 --> 00:13:40.547 line:82%
Dinner at 8... 8... Dinner!

206
00:13:41.042 --> 00:13:43.165 line:82%
- Dinner at 8
- Yeah.

207
00:13:43.256 --> 00:13:45.288 line:82%
AII right. I'm going to
pick you up at 7.30.

208
00:13:45.375 --> 00:13:50.333 line:82%
Poor Rohit,
he wasn't as cool as he thought he was.

209
00:13:52.172 --> 00:13:53.273 line:82%
But...

210
00:13:54.874 --> 00:13:55.955 line:82%
He never stopped trying.

211
00:14:07.645 --> 00:14:10.167 line:82%
- Hey Gorgeous!
- Are you taIking to me?

212
00:14:10.625 --> 00:14:12.690 line:82%
Who else?
You think I was talking to him?

213
00:14:14.042 --> 00:14:15.125 line:82%
My name is Rohit.

214
00:14:15.667 --> 00:14:19.437 line:82%
- Don't bother. I'm married...
- So what?

215
00:14:19.542 --> 00:14:21.875 line:82%
-So what if you are married--
-...to him.

216
00:14:24.974 --> 00:14:30.375 line:82%
- I'm sorry. I didn't mean it.
- Put him down.

217
00:14:32.900 --> 00:14:35.127 line:82%
